ast whether there is a need to be more ruthless in their assessment, Goh said: \\\"We do not want to just be comfortable with that performance in Hangzhou.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1400, \"end\": 1408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.934226022683058e-18, \"text\": \"Hangzhou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the podcast\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"a need\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"their assessment\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"Goh\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"that performance\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But we say successful contextually because we see the trajectory and potential of where we can go.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the trajectory\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"potential\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But yes, I agree with you, we should be ruthless about it.\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We should not be satisfied.\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's not the attitude and posture we want Team Singapore to have coming out of Hangzhou, we want them to be hungrier.\\\"\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1651, \"end\": 1660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9999999979399945, \"rank\": 2.059979553418517e-09, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}, {\"begin\": 1683, \"end\": 1691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.934226022683058e-18, \"text\": \"Hangzhou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the attitude\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1625}, {\"ngram\": \"posture\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He highlighted how swimmer Letitia Sim, 20, exemplified that ruthless approach.\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1803, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"how swimmer Letitia Sim\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1762}, {\"ngram\": \"that ruthless approach\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sim missed out on an Asiad medal three times in China but managed to pick herself up.\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1825, \"end\": 1830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Asiad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1852, \"end\": 1857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9102537831798161, \"rank\": 0.09858645860511892, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sim\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Japan Open in November, she became Singapore's first female swimmer to meet the qualifying time for the Paris Olympics in the 100m breaststroke while also setting a new national record.\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 2083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1933, \"end\": 1942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9999999979399945, \"rank\": 2.059979553418517e-09, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.o