\": 3245}, {\"ngram\": \"Su\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3281}, {\"ngram\": \"an exciting journey\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2023, she bagged the 100m-200m double at the SEA Games and Asian championships, before adding the 200m gold in Hangzhou.\", \"from\": 3363, \"to\": 3486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3425, \"end\": 3430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.297787979446252e-20, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 3477, \"end\": 3485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.934226022683058e-18, \"text\": \"Hangzhou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the SEA Games\", \"from\": 3407, \"to\": 3420}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m gold\", \"from\": 3460, \"to\": 3473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also reached the 200m semi-finals of the world championships, which earned her a spot at Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 200m semi\", \"from\": 3505, \"to\": 3518}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 3519, \"to\": 3525}, {\"ngram\": \"the world championships\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3552}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3577}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 3581, \"to\": 3586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was her first qualification on merit for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3650, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her first qualification\", \"from\": 3600, \"to\": 3623}, {\"ngram\": \"merit\", \"from\": 3627, \"to\": 3632}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3637, \"to\": 3649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Su said: \\\"She is only beginning to discover where we can break through and she is quietly working together with Luis (Cunha), with the team who continue to prime her in good shape.\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3832, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Su\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3654}, {\"ngram\": \"Luis\", \"from\": 3764, \"to\": 3768}, {\"ngram\": \"(Cunha\", \"from\": 3769, \"to\": 3775}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3791}, {\"ngram\": \"good shape\", \"from\": 3821, \"to\": 3831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let us watch this space, let us cheer her on and get excited.\\\"\", \"from\": 3834, \"to\": 3897, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3839, \"to\": 3841}, {\"ngram\": \"this space\", \"from\": 3848, \"to\": 3858}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3864, \"to\": 3866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team Singapore had won medals from the 2008 to 2016 Olympics, but returned home empty-handed from the Tokyo Games in 2021.\", \"from\": 3899, \"to\": 4021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Team Singapore\", \"from\": 3899, \"to\": 3913}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 3922, \"to\": 3928}, {\"ngram\": \"2016 Olympics\", \"from\": 3946, \"to\": 3959}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 3997, \"to\": 4012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beyond individual athletic performances, Goh also highlighted an active sporting calendar in 2024.\", \"from\": 4023, \"to\": 4121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"individual athletic performances\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4062}, {\"ngram\": \"Goh\", \"from\": 4064, \"to\": 4067}, {\"ngram\": \"an active sporting calendar\", \"from\": 4085, \"to\": 4112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Singapore will host table tennis' Singapore Smash in March, the Professional Triathletes Organisation Asian Open in April and World Rugby HSBC SVNS in May.\", \"from\": 4122, \"to\": 4277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4122, \"end\": 4131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9999999979399945, \"rank\": 2.059979553418517e-09, \"text\": \"Singapore